This is a C library for opening images in any format.

File "iio.c" contains all the functions.
File "iio.h" contains (part of) the API and some documentation.

The files "misc/*.c" are example programs.

The philosophy underlying the library is described on file "doc/iio.txt".

The directory "samples" contains sample images in various formats.

The "misc/fes*" files are (tentative) build scripts for different conditions.

Cmake helpers are located on "contrib/cmake"

Python bindings are located on "contrib/piio_packaged"
